# Vite picks up VITE_* prefixed vars from .env.local (gitignored). Copy this
# file to .env.local and fill in real values to enable Drive integration.
#
# 1. Google Cloud project: enable "Google Drive API" and "Google Picker API".
# 2. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application). Add http://localhost:5173
#    to "Authorized JavaScript origins" for local dev, plus your prod origin.
# 3. Create a Browser API Key, restricted to your origin(s) and the two APIs above.
#
# The local-file path works without these.

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
